Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now you'll be saying\Ngoodbye to your johnny, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Your luck ran out when you met me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:15.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello? I'm busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We'll take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Stay here and feel ashamed\Nof yourself until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:46.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(303,372)}Episode 6:\NEden of the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is this the right place to drop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you come with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I know, but I'll go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:07.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bring everyone over\Nwith you, then. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Morimi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki? Hurry up and come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:37.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No. I'm too ashamed to see Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ryosuke's not angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to come home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWhere are you now, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,At Micchon's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay with her for a while,\Nso don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, you come home right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's not like we don't know where she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so let's let her alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Gotta apologize to Osugi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Would you lend me some clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(99,259)}Eden\Nof\Nthe\NEast
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess maybe this sounds fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You couldn't call it anything but fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You should probably go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:54.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, it's hard to\Nswallow this Takizawa's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure about that\Noutfit you're wearing, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:01.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?\NSaki looks good in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:06.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And I think this Takizawa thing\Nis actually pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's absurd,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:14.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but it's not like Saki living with him\Nor not is the only issue here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:19.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This club's about to hit the end\Nof the road if nothing changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,To think that not only our\Nclub's attention-grabber,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but the entire elite staff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:31.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,would all show interest in\Nsuch a dubious character!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:36.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Just what's happened with you\Nsince the graduation trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:40.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This behavior just doesn't seem\Nworthy of the seasoned maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,who's easily parried the come-ons of Osugi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and all the other youthful Johnnys\Nwith blood surging in their loins
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,for a full four years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did something special happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--Surging blood aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,if we'd successfully started our business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,you wanted to keep Saki here come\Nhell or high water, right, Kazuomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:06.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,After all, Eden only worked because\NSaki compensated for your one weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,your lack of leadership skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now hold on. I don't mind\Nyou criticizing my faults,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but don't you think there's a huge difference
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,between me and what that\NTakizawa person is saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We may have been forced\Ninto temporary withdrawal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:25.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but I am steadily moving forward\Nwith starting the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Whereas he has no clothes and no memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:31.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and can't remember his family, his job,\Nor even what movies he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:35.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I won't have you comparing me to\Nsomeone who has absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Poor boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:43.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if his personal.44 Magnum\Nis still at the mercy of that cold wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hirasawa, from what I've\Nbeen hearing from in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:07:00.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't believe Mr. Takizawa\Nis as worthless as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's always been gentlemanly\Nand broad-minded towards Morimi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and he has the drive to act, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,His house is a shopping mall,\Nso he seems to have some wealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and most importantly, there is no\Nsuch thing as an evil dog owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want your opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sitting here and talking about it is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:23.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go meet him\Nand see what he's really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:29.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Agreed! Seeing is believing.\NLet's go size him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You've got a point, but we have\Nto be prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:37.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate in secret first,\Nand not just go in through the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What the heck? That's so passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Call it "cautious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:50.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought maybe I\Ncould completely believe in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but I am a little scared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:02.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll go get a car. We'll leave in a half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hirasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:11.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is, Osugi treated me to\Na first-class dinner last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And after hearing Morimi's story,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:17.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I figured out something that\NI didn't realize at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:21.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That dinner must have been\Noriginally planned with Morimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?! Why didn't you tell me sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say this in front of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Plus, judging from how\Nhe was acting at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:36.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Osugi definitely saw Morimi with Mr. Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And what did Osugi do after dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He disappeared into the night, blind drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And now it seems even Morimi\Ncan't get in touch with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:53.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We can't leave Osugi out in the cold\Non such an important occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,True, even if he did skip out\Non us while he was job hunting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,he is an important charter member.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:03.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,However, this is also a golden\Nopportunity to keep Saki in Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,All right, find Osugi and\Nhold him in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is his house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any other entrances?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:41.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, because there\Nwere no homeless people inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:45.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This could so easily be a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess we've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki, you might be marrying into money here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:10:00.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Property values around here fell\Npretty sharply after Careless Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:05.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now, we don't know that he bought\Nthis place after the missile strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey, hold everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This place is a gold mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--It's so cute!\N--It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't go messing with those\Nand getting us into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa lives in the VIP room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:52.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We've come this far, so why don't you\Nsay a few words to him as our rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--What's wrong?\N--Where's Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:36.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Not there. But the man's had us\Nunder surveillance all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's best not to get involved\Nwith such a dubious character!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who's a dubious character?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This Takizawa person, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Happy to have you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:08.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh my, he has wings! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This title deed is the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I just found it today, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I more or less understand what you've said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:25.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but what exactly made you\Ndecide to support our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And more fundamentally,\Nwhat are your intentions for Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No particular "intentions",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I just thought there was no\Nneed for her to work for men
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:35.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,who would up and dump beef bowls on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:41.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If everyone, not just Saki, became NEETs,\Nwe could turn this country around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Those old guys who take it\Nfor granted they're the winners
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:47.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,will freak out and come crying to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:54.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why not? Didn't you\Nbasically have the same idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I saw Eden of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is really well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(271,170)\fn\fs18}[Harumi Bridge]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:02.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Would you call it an "image search engine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I tried entering that miniature Shiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(371,169)}[Mini Shiba]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and it recognizes him no matter\Nwhat angle I take a pic from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307,357)\fn\fs18}[Akira Takizawa's Buddy]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:07.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(390,411)}[Name: Unknown]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's the one who wrote the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:16.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? You're smart, Mittan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's got a sharp tongue\Nwhen she's among friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:21.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but she's always like this with strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:26.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,As a kid, she never played with anyone\Nbut Hirasawa, her cousin, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I-I'm  not "Mittan."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:35.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So if you register something on the site,\Nany cell phone can use the info.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is pretty cool.
