Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(443,50)}[Kaiuomi Hirasawa]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(407,334)}[Soji University\NEconomics Department]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(402,368)}[Born 1989]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(352,22)}[Kazuomi Hirasawa]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(220,78)}[Micchon's Cousin]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(248,260)}[Soji University\NEconomics Department]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(245,361)}[Born in 1989]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki told me. If you pulled\Noff this great an invention,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,it must've seemed like a good\Nidea to turn it into a business,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so why didn't that go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:09.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't need you if I end up having\Nto take care of things anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:15.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Honestly, the road ahead\Nis long... in a lot of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Juiz.\N--Yes, this is Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:25.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I need a secretary fluent in French\Nand Cantonese, on the double.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:29.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Accepted. Noblesse oblige.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I sincerely pray that you,\Nthe most hardworking of CEOs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,will be an innovative savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You don't need to show up\Ntomorrow, or ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:45.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,CEO Shiratori is in a dark mood today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,To make the story short,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,we just had a little trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:56.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,of the sort that can happen\Non any site or message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,One girl had the misfortune\Nof having to leave school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and the university opened an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--How about this?\N--That?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Hey, I thought it was nice.\N--No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We started out as a little recycling community,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but thanks to the development\Nof the image recognition engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:24.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,even near-junk turned into valuable goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Because Saki wrote new value into the images
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:29.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that others would never have dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then the rest of our members copied her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and at some point students\Nthemselves started being registered,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:43.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and people found Eden useful\Nas a tool for finding love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And that's what caused the "trouble"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What with one thing and another,\Nwe had one member quit to look for work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:55.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and Saki had to leave home for some\Nreason none of us know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of how useless I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We're going home, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:06.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why? Did you and Takky\Nnot come to an agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I am a NEET, but I've always prided\Nmyself on being one of the best NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:14.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't have any special\Nskills like Saki or Micchon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I've studied management and law,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:20.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,to become an elite NEET that\Ncould back up other elite NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And you succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Almost, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then what are you hung up on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Eden of the East is a paradise for NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:33.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get help from\Nsomeone who's not a NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:40.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Think of it as the jealousy of a\N"have-not" for one of the "haves."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I get you... not that I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,As someone with no memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've got my own complicated\Nworries I can't tell anyone about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm actually the one who wants your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:57.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think? I can't explain\Nthe circumstances right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:01.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but would you help me carry out\Nmy obligations as a "have"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:04.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My funding offer can be your compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:08.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please, Hirasawa. I'll prepare myself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll help run Eden with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:18.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki's what troubled you the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's left to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So in the end, I'm saved by Saki again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's no big deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's do a sort of give-and-take thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:39.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I still don't completely trust you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:42.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but right now I'll shake your hand, Mr. Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, from now on, I'm just calling you "Takizawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:49.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Let's make this a NEET paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:53.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yay! Now that's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:58.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takizawa. You didn't\Njust help me, you helped everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No worries. I really like people like Hirasawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:04.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,who are working to help other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:12.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, can I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:15.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you tell me to "come to your place"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hadn't told you about everyone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were looking for a change of clothes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think these would look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Micchon is playing and having fun\Nwith some guy she just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:55.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Though it's less like "playing" and\Nmore like he's messing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Come on, if you don't stick it in\Nmore firmly, it'll just flip over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,...Mittan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:06.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't do it that well. And I'm not "Mittan"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What've you been setting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:50.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're such a scaredy-cat, Mittan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:54.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not "Mittan."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Kasuga. Have you found Osugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:18.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like I kind of have,\Nand I kind of haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:25.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is, it's possible\NOsugi's run into the "Johnny Hunter."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The Johnny Hunter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was digging around on\Nthe internet looking for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:33.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and I found some very interesting\Nentries on a certain message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why look for Osugi on the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I know, but a man who says he's been\Nimprisoned by a suspicious woman
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,has been intermittently posting cries for help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,for the last eighteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like the police\Nare doing anything yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:51.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but there's quite a commotion online.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:55.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And no matter how I look at it,\NI think this has to be Osugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Send me the URL of this message board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay. Rumors are that the Johnny Hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,has already claimed a full 20,000 victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:09.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so it wouldn't be odd for\NOsugi to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future